review_blob: God damm this Cristmas beer is good.  And yes the cork is a b#$ch to get out.  Alcohol yes, with a taste of apricot.  Wow it tast like a dried apricot.
For some it may be sweet; very sweet.  But when I am in the mood one of these is perfect, emphasis on ONE.  Caramel/Custard aroma and taste...the question lingers, how do they make this beer?
